<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1899-04-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1899-04-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="73" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d73">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bridgman</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">La Paz, Bolivia</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-04-20"><hi rend="italic">April
                                        20, 1899</hi></date>.</dateline>
                            <seg rendition="#left">No. 115.]</seg></opener>
                        <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to report that I received
                            on April 17 the following cablegram from the Department: <quote rend="blockquote">
                                <p>On request British Government you will protect British subjects
                                    and interests if necessary. Notify Bolivian authorities.</p>
                                <p rend="right"><hi rend="smallcaps">Hay.</hi></p>
                            </quote>
                        </p>
                        <pb facs="0200" n="108" xml:id="pg_108"/>
                        <p>I will notify the Bolivian Government of the same as soon as
                            possible.</p>
                        <p>At present there is no need of protection, as everything is quiet. I have
                            in several instances protected British interests in the absence of any
                            English representative.</p>
                        <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">George H.
                            Bridgman.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>